# Katsumascore Design System - Project Structure

This is a WordPress theme design system built with React, TypeScript, SCSS, and Storybook following ITCSS methodology.

## Core Architecture

### Entry Points
- Main TypeScript entry: [src/ts/index.ts](mdc:src/ts/index.ts)
- Main SCSS entry: [src/scss/index.scss](mdc:src/scss/index.scss)
- Webpack config: [webpack.config.js](mdc:webpack.config.js)

### Directory Structure
```
src/
├── stories/           # Storybook stories and components
│   ├── components/    # Reusable UI components
│   ├── layouts/       # Layout components
│   ├── projects/      # Project-specific components
│   └── styles/        # Style documentation
├── scss/              # SCSS stylesheets (ITCSS)
│   ├── foundation/    # Reset, base styles
│   ├── global/        # Variables, mixins
│   ├── layout/        # Layout components
│   ├── object/        # UI components, utilities
│   ├── inc/           # Third-party styles
│   └── plugins/       # Plugin-specific styles
├── ts/                # TypeScript modules
├── assets/            # Static assets (images, icons)
└── admin/             # WordPress admin styles
```

### ITCSS SCSS Architecture
1. **Foundation**: [src/scss/foundation/](mdc:src/scss/foundation/) - Reset, base styles
2. **Global**: [src/scss/global/](mdc:src/scss/global/) - Variables, mixins, functions
3. **Layout**: [src/scss/layout/](mdc:src/scss/layout/) - Layout components
4. **Object**: [src/scss/object/](mdc:src/scss/object/) - UI components and utilities
5. **Inc**: [src/scss/inc/](mdc:src/scss/inc/) - Third-party styles
6. **Plugins**: [src/scss/plugins/](mdc:src/scss/plugins/) - Plugin-specific styles

### Build Output
- JavaScript: `dist/bundle.js` (development) or `dist/[name].[contenthash:8].js` (production)
- CSS: `dist/build.css` (development) or `dist/[name].[contenthash:8].css` (production)
- Assets: `dist/img/` directory for images

### Key Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [prettier.config.js](mdc:prettier.config.js) - Code formatting rules
